{"id": 1112, "genre": 1001, "title": "对自己的动手能力你都有过哪些错误的自信？", "description": "以为自己是鲁班，最后发现是手残。（题图来自：Viktoria Maliar）", "record_count": 2206, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607102121292yqsR6ub9zowQErk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-28T03:09:54Z", "options": [{"id": 102400, "content": "宜家灯具有什么难的 自己买了一堆铁丝和布 却总也达不出能站稳的结构", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668003}, {"id": 102401, "content": "以为自己买的衣服最后搭配起来一定是自己想象的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693686}, {"id": 102402, "content": "总以为自己一定能剪出满意的刘海，然后…", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693686}, {"id": 102403, "content": "以为能够一打五，然后我就动了手?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694435}, {"id": 103427, "content": "动手是啥 ???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698138}, {"id": 102404, "content": "以为自己可以把电脑拆了又原样安回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517396}, {"id": 102405, "content": "这作业用不了多长时间就能写完???", "image": null, "praise_count": 322, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611678}, {"id": 102406, "content": "总觉得自己守望先锋打得好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 102918, "content": "拆闹钟拆音响的时候坚信自己能装回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683774}, {"id": 102407, "content": "拿只铅笔，以为照着素描书，就能画个苹果了", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423267}, {"id": 102408, "content": "科科 那些好看的照片不就是靠修图嘛 我也可以拍出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154367}, {"id": 102409, "content": "砌墙码砖看着简单，可要码的整齐有美感还是挺难的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530601}, {"id": 102410, "content": "3D拼图多简单分分钟的事 咦这伦敦塔桥怎么歪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165506}, {"id": 102411, "content": "以为自己能够打一手好鼓，然后败在了课业作业手下", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694482}, {"id": 102412, "content": "按部就班学做菜，结果只能自食\"恶果\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694495}, {"id": 102413, "content": "以为自己能在家做双皮奶，最后发现做出来的只是浆糊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170904}, {"id": 102925, "content": "以为自己还能背出来 凤凰台，2句过后什么都不记得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696801}, {"id": 102415, "content": "别的不说，动手能力还是很强的，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674429}, {"id": 102418, "content": "单车掉链", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436005}, {"id": 102420, "content": "以为可以自己搭配衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693143}, {"id": 107542, "content": "以为自己是说干就干的类型，其实患有拖延症，拖着拖着就不想做了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711274}, {"id": 102423, "content": "看了很多美妆视频，以为自己能画好，结果给室友化成了熊猫眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600246}, {"id": 105751, "content": "练字吧 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707514}, {"id": 102424, "content": "以为做饭很简单，结果～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694529}, {"id": 102425, "content": "以为做饭很简单，结果～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694529}, {"id": 103449, "content": "总是认为自己是绘画高手，结果每次都是半途而废，即使这样也没关系，下一次再画", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698152}, {"id": 102426, "content": "总是三分钟热度", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689404}, {"id": 102427, "content": "以为可以在暑假好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690837}, {"id": 102429, "content": "从网上买一大堆零件，准备自己组装，结果。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689070}, {"id": 106781, "content": "认为自己也能做出大神级的菜，但最后做出了一堆“精致的垃圾”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 102431, "content": "写情书", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685351}, {"id": 102432, "content": "拆iphone5s换电池，然后把指纹拆坏了秒变iphone5", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257121}, {"id": 102433, "content": "?????", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694561}, {"id": 102434, "content": "Nike ID自己设计半天\n最后还是买了官方的设计", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341793}, {"id": 102435, "content": "给自己涂指甲油", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684638}, {"id": 102436, "content": "我能瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687332}, {"id": 102438, "content": "编辫子，自认为不会乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688429}, {"id": 102439, "content": "数字油画不就是涂色游戏嘛，so easy。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171070}, {"id": 102695, "content": "觉得自己已经做得很好啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694600}, {"id": 102440, "content": "做菜居然还要放味精？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529479}, {"id": 102696, "content": "觉得自己已经尽力啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694600}, {"id": 102441, "content": "嗯，我的无人机还挂在墙上，大半年了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430908}, {"id": 102442, "content": "总以为能用手撑起身体早早起床……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182221}, {"id": 102443, "content": "设计汽车", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694623}, {"id": 102444, "content": "素描只停留在线条和正方形上  硬伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86649}, {"id": 102700, "content": "日语很容易上手，然后学了两年都没学会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695336}, {"id": 102446, "content": "考试能拿第一", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694636}, {"id": 102958, "content": "再玩会手机吧，没事，明早能起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690235}, {"id": 102447, "content": "化妆啊，以为自己能变网红脸，结果，还是那个傻样乡村样", "image": "img/option/option/20160728155533Sjr8v7GPzU3W4Lbl.jpeg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690126}, {"id": 102449, "content": "以为可以弯一个手机架", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693625}]}